videos.description: Dwayne Bacon finds the cutting Jonathan Isaac who throws it down for FSU.
videos.headline: FSU's Isaac finishes with the powerful jam

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac comes up with the big rejection that leads to a dunk off the miss by Jarquez Smith.
videos.headline: FSU's Isaac gets the big rejection

videos.description: PJ Savoy finds Dwayne Bacon who slams it in for the Seminoles.
videos.headline: FSU's Bacon flies high for the big jam

videos.description: Jonathan Issac comes up with the steal and Dwayne Bacon feeds him for the wide open jam.
videos.headline: Isaac throws one down after the steal

videos.description: Braian Angola-Rodas gives the lob to Jarquez Smith who finishes with the big dunk.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Smith with the thunderous alley-oop jam in win

videos.headline: FSU's Forrest tries to destroy the rim with vicious dunk
